# Styling Contracts for UI/UX Upgrade

## CSS Custom Properties (Theme Variables)

### Color Variables
- `--ifm-color-primary`: Primary brand color
- `--ifm-color-primary-dark`: Darker shade of primary
- `--ifm-color-primary-darker`: Even darker shade
- `--ifm-color-primary-darkest`: Darkest shade
- `--ifm-color-primary-light`: Lighter shade of primary
- `--ifm-color-primary-lighter`: Even lighter shade
- `--ifm-color-primary-lightest`: Lightest shade
- `--ifm-color-secondary`: Secondary color
- `--ifm-color-success`: Success state color
- `--ifm-color-info`: Information state color
- `--ifm-color-warning`: Warning state color
- `--ifm-color-danger`: Error state color

### Typography Variables
- `--ifm-font-family-base`: Base font family
- `--ifm-font-size-base`: Base font size
- `--ifm-line-height-base`: Base line height
- `--ifm-heading-font-family`: Heading font family
- `--ifm-heading-font-weight`: Heading font weight

### Spacing Variables
- `--ifm-spacing-vertical`: Vertical spacing unit
- `--ifm-spacing-horizontal`: Horizontal spacing unit
- `--ifm-global-radius`: Border radius
- `--ifm-global-shadow`: Box shadow

## Component Class Customization Points

### Navigation Components
- `.navbar`: Main navigation bar styling
- `.navbar__brand`: Logo/branding area customization
- `.navbar__items`: Navigation items container
- `.menu`: Sidebar menu styling
- `.menu__link`: Menu links customization
- `.menu__list`: Menu list items styling

### Content Components
- `.main-wrapper`: Main content wrapper
- `.container`: Content container styling
- `.markdown`: Markdown content styling
- `.theme-code-block`: Code block styling
- `.alert`: Alert/callout components styling

### Layout Components
- `.footer`: Footer component styling
- `.hero`: Hero section styling (if used)
- `.table-of-contents`: Table of contents styling

## Responsive Design Specifications
- `--ifm-container-width`: Maximum container width
- `--ifm-container-width-xl`: Extra large container width
- Mobile-first responsive approach with appropriate breakpoints

## Accessibility Standards
- Focus state styling for keyboard navigation
- Proper color contrast ratios (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Semantic HTML structure preservation
- Screen reader compatibility